Layout Example using table:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>HTML Layouts Application</title>
    </head
    <body>
        <table width="100%" border="0">
            <tr>
                <td align="center" colspan="100%" bgcolor="#c0c0c0"><h3>HTML Layouts Application</h3></td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td width="20" bgcolor="#cee3f6">
                    <b>Topics</b><br />
                    JavaScript<br />
                    Java<br />
                    HTML<br />
                    CSS
                </td>
                <td bgcolor="#ffffff" width="200" height="150">
                    The Introduction of the website...<br />
                    Hello, YouTubers. Welcome to software developer channel. Learn free tutorials.
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td colspan="100" bgcolor="#c0c0c0">
                    <center>
                        <footer>Copyright &copy; 2016 softwaredeveloper.com</footer>
                    </center>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </body>
</html>

Layout Example using div containers:

<body>
        <div style="width:100%">
                <div align="center" style="background-color:#c0c0c0; height:10%; width:100%"><h3>HTML Layouts Application</h3></div>
                <div style="background-color:#cee3f6; float:left; width:20%">
                    <div><b>Topics</b></div>
                    JavaScript<br />
                    Java<br />
                    HTML<br />
                    CSS
                </div>
                <div style="background-color:#ffffff"; width="200" height="100">
                    The Introduction of the website...<br />
                    Hello, YouTubers. Welcome to software developer channel. Learn free tutorials.
                </div>
                <div style="background-color:#c0c0c0; clear:both">
                    <center>
                        <footer>Copyright &copy; 2016 softwaredeveloper.com</footer>
                    </center>
                </div>
        </div>
    </body>
